Package: SVMFeature
Type: Package
Language: en-US
Title: Multiobjective SVMs with Feature Selection via NSGA-II
Version: 0.1.0
Description: An R package for solving the multiobjective soft-margin support vector machine with feature selection problem. The current version implements an NSGA-II-based metaheuristic for Pareto frontier approximation, together with tools for model assessment, visualization, and reproducible computational experiments.
